welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Victor, a charming city known for its beautiful landscapes and friendly locals. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that this charming destination has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Greater Rochester International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is primarily used for domestic flights, with a few international flights operated by Air Canada.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B serves as the hub for Delta Air Lines, with most of their domestic and international flights departing from here.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, with no time limit or data cap.
